column5: Traveling to Ontario at the end of May. Does anyone know of or have a link to a place that I can find out what food products might be restricted? I think last year it was potatoes, or lettuce....can't remember.... Anyway, thanks in advance. John
Potatoes, dog food, and a few other things I can't remember. I'll see if I can find the link.http://www.infonorth.net/
